ules only'=>'Enkel handmatige regels','Web Application Firewall'=>'Web applicatie firewall','Plus on-demand manual scans'=>'Plus on-demand handmatige scans','Daily automated scans'=>'Dagelijkse geautomatiseerde scans','Line by line malware scanning'=>'Malwarescanning per regel','Check items against database'=>'Items controleren aan de hand van de database','Scan for threats and vulnerabilities'=>'Scan op dreigingen en kwetsbaarheden','Generate text, tables, and lists'=>'Genereer tekst, tabellen en lijsten','Jetpack AI Assistant brings the power of AI right into your WordPress editor, letting your content creation soar to new heights.'=>'Jetpack AI Assistant brengt de kracht van AI rechtstreeks naar je WordPress-editor, waardoor je inhoud creatie naar nieuwe hoogten stijgt.','<p>Paid customers get dedicated email support from our world-class Happiness Engineers to help with any issue.</p>
